official_title: A bill to amend title XIV of the Housing and Urban Development Act of 1968 (the Interstate Land Sales Full Disclosure Act) to provide for the exemption of new communities from the requirements of that title.

summary.text: Sets forth criteria for the exemption of new communities from the requirements of the Interstate Land Sales Full Disclosure Act.
